    a4 = -c4/48,
    a6 = -c6/864,
and returns the transformed and factored triple {c4, c6, Delta}.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.990668485703532*^9, {3.990668559439372*^9, 
   3.9906685680455847`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c62dac0c-3877-4598-93b4-\
df0b41e6a68f"],

