Cell[TextData[{
 "We have obtained,  \nProvisional p - sig (E3) = (m,m,2m) where m=",
 Cell[BoxData[
  SubscriptBox["\[Nu]", "p"]],
  CellChangeTimes->{3.886252756526535*^9},ExpressionUUID->
  "359fed19-54c0-42a0-a6ec-e323217cccc9"],
 "(t+27)\nLet be m=6n+k (k=0,1,2,3), then\n         p-sig(E3)=(2 k+s,s,2 s)\n \
   Iso=p^n --\[Rule] p-minimal \n        p-sig(E3)=(k,2n+2k,3k)\
\[LineSeparator]    k = 0 -- -> (2k,0, 0) -- > I_0\n   k = 1 -- -> (1+2 \
k,1,2)--> II\n    k = 2-- -> (2+2 k,2,4) -> IV\n    k = 3 -- -> (3+2 k,3,6)-- \
> I_0^*\n    k = 4 -- -> (4+2 k,4,8)-- > IV^*\n    k = 5-- -> (5+2 k,5,10)-- \
> II^*\n    \n   "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8881433308879223`*^9, 3.888143374571212*^9}, {
   3.888143571828759*^9, 3.8881436034019003`*^9}, {3.8881436884055853`*^9, 
