  SubscriptBox["\[Nu]", "2"]],
  CellChangeTimes->{3.886252756526535*^9},ExpressionUUID->
  "2e9f9e85-c899-432d-bd14-6938bb06cd12"],
 "(a+61)=n-2\n\nprovisional 2 - sig (E1) = (4+(n-2)+(m-2), 5+(m-2),4+2(m-2))"
}], "Text",
